<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Thank You | EcoThrift</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f8f5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: 100vh;
    }

    .thankyou-container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 60px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .thankyou-container h2 {
      color: #2e7d32;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .thankyou-container p {
      color: #555;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .thankyou-container .btn {
      background-color: #2e7d32;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .thankyou-container .btn:hover {
      background-color: #1b5e20;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .thankyou-container {
        padding: 30px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="thankyou-container">
    <h2>Thank You for Your Donation!</h2>
    <p>Your thoughtful contribution helps extend the life of pre-loved items and supports communities in need through our partnered NGOs.</p>
    <a href="index.jsp" class="btn">Back to Home</a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
